RESULT

Company Name: ModuloTech

Company Website: http://www.modulotech.fr

Contact Person: Randja Yazid

Product:   moduloTech is a company founded in 2011 whose reputation has been built around the following concepts dear to its founders: 

The first concept is an extreme attention paid to the user experience which must be in service of the perfect and extremely simple use of their applications. 

The second around a recognized pro-activity in the sectors where they evolve. They are very proud to have more outgoing calls than incoming calls to support. 

The third, a completely liberated management which advocates total freedom of enterprise for their employees. Their only daily objective is to serve the vision of the company and ensure that each member of the team is involved in the project. They advocate the autonomy, development, personal and professional development of each employee, thanks to their unique management method called "moduloCracy"! 

They are a tight-knit team, and publish several services with a unified vision mainly focused on process optimization and user experience, particularly in the home automation and automotive sector.

Country-Location: France

Target Audience: worldwide

Immediate Requirement: Randja is looking for Mobile Developer (Android, IOS)

Next Step: send all information about our company, we need to find candidates for Randja. 

Next Contact Date: keep in touch by email
